      "S1: Normal Operations (83%)           13,800,081      26,800,042      13,800,081\n",
      "S2: Partial Grounding (58%)           21,600,057      29,400,034      21,600,057\n",
      "S3: Crisis – Severe Grounding (33%)      29,400,034      29,400,034      29,400,034\n",
      "===============================================================================================\n",
      "Worst-case Minimax bound: 29,400,034.00\n",
